      • RESTART_STRATEGY

        @PublicEvolving
public static final String RESTART_STRATEGY
        Defines the restart strategy to be used. It can be "off", "none", "disable" to be disabled or it can be "fixeddelay", "fixed-delay" to use the FixedDelayRestartStrategy or it can be "failurerate", "failure-rate" to use FailureRateRestartStrategy. You can also specify a class name which implements the RestartStrategy interface and has a static create method which takes a Configuration object.
